# CodeQL ignore patterns - exclude non-Python files from analysis

# Documentation
**/*.md
docs/
README.md
CHANGELOG.md
CONTRIBUTING.md

# Configuration files
**/*.yml
**/*.yaml
**/*.json
.github/
.vscode/
.gitignore

# Templates and examples (not runnable code)
**/templates/
**/examples/
**/*-template.*
**/*-example.*

# Dependencies
node_modules/
venv/
.venv/
env/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Build output
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/

# IDE
.idea/
.history/
